## BACKEND ROUTES

Build these REST endpoints:

**Auth**
- POST /api/auth/login → returns JWT
- POST /api/auth/logout

**Admins** (super_admin only for write)
- GET /api/admins
- POST /api/admins
- DELETE /api/admins/:id

**Members**
- GET /api/members (supports query params: province, taskforce, age_range, search)
- POST /api/members
- PUT /api/members/:id
- DELETE /api/members/:id

**Events**
- GET /api/events
- POST /api/events
- PUT /api/events/:id
- DELETE /api/events/:id

**Event Files**
- POST /api/events/:id/files (multer upload)
- GET /api/events/:id/files
- DELETE /api/files/:id

**Contributions**
- GET /api/contributions?event_id=X
- PUT /api/contributions (upsert by event_id + member_id)

**Messages**
- POST /api/messages/send (validates WA, queues sends, logs results)
- GET /api/messages/campaigns
- GET /api/messages/campaigns/:id/log

**WhatsApp**
- GET /api/whatsapp/status
- GET /api/whatsapp/qr (returns QR as base64 image)
- POST /api/whatsapp/disconnect

